      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "I adore the art direction of these remakes. Some people may see it as overly simplistic but after playing many remakes of classic 90s platformers that fills the game with superfluous detail to make it fit visually with today’s games (calling you out specifically "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Spyro: Reignited Trilogy"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " and your unnecessarily large patches of grass that obscure collectables), it is a much needed breath of fresh air. It keeps the feel of the original game’s graphics and art style without losing any detail."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Now, this isn’t the first time "
