        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          " "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "back in 2009. While this version reviewed well, one constant criticism was its voice acting, at least for the English version, that is. It wasn’t bad by any means; it was just considered strange to redub the game’s original "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Banjo-Kazooie"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "-esque barks. These remakes get around that by using the original audio and even compressing them in the same way the original games did to retain the feeling of playing a classic platformer from the 90s and these additions carry over to "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
